{"tid":649943,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"係穩定之中想搵啲衝擊","createTime":"2018-05-02T02:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T00:47:41.000Z","uid":156995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b520af1b658a01f38aa396a23e8b45f1a675c2","tid":649943,"uid":156995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"而家返緊一份都算好穩定嘅工<br />\n即係只要你唔辭職佢又唔會炒你嗰啲<br />\n人工一般，餓你唔死又飽你唔親<br />\n總之就安安穩穩但係搵多啲錢又無我份嗰啲<br />\n因為返放工時間好穩定，所以就想搵啲野搞<br />\n想做下小生意又無咩諗法<br />\n錢又唔係儲得多，投資又唔到我<br />\n有無人同我一樣咁迷惘"},{"pid":"7a6c12b0e0723cf93de6b1666963f4cb258d89ef","tid":649943,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:17:15.000Z","msg":"今晚利物浦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c238cd28c2aa5cfabbe282d64ce44c960f98ef85","tid":649943,"uid":46128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 餓唔死, 無發達, 無出路, 無前途"},{"pid":"c362f400a78da57898011ed067b9a2c17bdc3420","tid":649943,"uid":156995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚利物浦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔賭㗎我，得嗰雞碎咁多，大錢都唔輪到我"},{"pid":"c1af0e998f1ad254bf3e45cc7997f661d1985444","tid":649943,"uid":156995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 餓唔死, 無發達, 無出路, 無前途</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想襯時間多自己搵下出路"},{"pid":"52fc3d5d0f276306cf30343ad374c9ce9e5a6e06",